f2f4e59083b1'),(835,202,'processes_1_text','Our state-of-the art finishing booth allows us to make finish samples for approval by clients or replicate any desired finish, removing any doubts from their minds as to whether their end product will have the finish they demand. We can strip any paint or stain and leave faded, tarnished furniture looking new. Additionally, we can make reproductions of any antique furniture finishes if desired. We have hundreds of samples in our showrooms to choose from. We ceruse oak and bleach mahogany by hand-scraping the wood. This process gives the wood a rustic, more traditional look.'),(836,202,'_processes_1_text','field_5f2f4e66083b3'),(837,283,'_wp_attached_file','2020/08/finishing-double-image-scaled.jpg'),(838,283,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:1920;s:6:\"height\";i:2560;s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"2020/08/finishing-double-image-scaled.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:7:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:35:\"finishing-double-image-768x1024.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:1024;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:34:\"finishing-double-image-640x640.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:640;s:6:\"height\";i:640;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:35:\"finishing-double-image-768x1024.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:1024;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:9:\"1536x1536\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"finishing-double-image-1152x1536.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1152;s:6:\"height\";i:1536;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:9:\"2048x2048\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"finishing-double-image-1536x2048.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1536;s:6:\"height\";i:2048;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:21:\"woocommerce_thumbnail\";a:6:{s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"finishing-double-image-scaled-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:42027;s:9:\"uncropped\";b:0;}s:29:\"woocommerce_gallery_thumbnail\";a