rames leaves them stronger and makes for a better finished product. Old cushions can be re-stuffed with new foam cores or filled in with down. Clients never have to worry about the integrity of the frame, finish of the legs or the cushions because we take care of everything under one roof!'),(858,202,'_processes_3_text','field_5f2f4e66083b3'),(859,202,'processes_3_link','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"View our Projects\";s:3:\"url\";s:42:\"https://lqustg.wpengine.com/re-upholstery/\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(860,202,'_processes_3_link','field_5f2f543534fa8'),(861,286,'_wp_attached_file','2020/08/upholstery-crop.jpg'),(862,286,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:612;s:6:\"height\";i:792;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2020/08/upholstery-crop.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"upholstery-crop-612x640.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:612;s:6:\"height\";i:640;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:21:\"woocommerce_thumbnail\";a:6:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"upholstery-crop-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:39829;s:9:\"uncropped\";b:0;}s:29:\"woocommerce_gallery_thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"upholstery-crop-100x100.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:100;s:6:\"height\";i:100;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:17307;}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(863,287,'_wp_attached_file','2020/08/IMG_7076-scaled.jpg'),(864,287,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:2560;s:6:\"height\";i:1706;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2020/08/IMG_7076-scaled.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:8:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"IMG_7076-1024x683.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s: